CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 28, 1959, pg. A18 reads: "Let's Have A Party! - A party was given recently for Carol Randall and Dorothy Haley at 7208 Kedron St.  Among the many guests who attended the party were the above: Arthur Slaughter, Garver Jackson, Sylvia Ostine, Paul Anderson, Billy Weathers, Margaret Burrell, James McCoy, John Carter, Netia Peoples, Earl Brown, Milton Fluellen, Joe Martin, Will Watson, Irvin Bailey, Eugene Washington, Joby Ramsey, Ted Harris, Ron Fields and Tom Canty.  The party was given by  the girls' parents, Mr. and Mrs. Randolph Randall and Mr. and Mrs. Dennis Haley. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of party guests of Carol Randall and Dorothy Haley including: Arthur Slaughter, Garver Jackson, Sylvia Ostine, Paul Anderson, Billy Weathers, Margaret Burrell, James McCoy, John Carter, Netia Peoples, Earl Brown, Milton Fluellen, Joe Martin, Will Watson, Irvin Bailey, Eugene Washington, Joby Ramsey, Ted Harris, Ron Fields, and Tom Canty posed in home at 7208 Kedron St.
